metadata.name: Curiosity Arise
metadata.description:
Warning!!! you might not be able to get some sleep after seeing this photo.

A simple triangle composition that makes your mind wonder about the story behind it. The cognitive friction is intense.

This piece is my most favorite in my A-list. My street photography journey started because of this photo. It gave me a lot of opportunities to connect to people with different race, culture, and belief. And it made me pursue what I really love to do.
